  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyPresentRemoteViewOfPlayerException
    Exception thrown when there is already the remote view that is supposed to be created
    FullChosenCardsException
    Exception thrown when deck of chosen gods is full
    InvalidBuildDomeException
    Exception thrown when there is already a dome in the position [row][col] selected
    InvalidIncrementLevelException
    Exception thrown when player try to build in a cell occupied
    InvalidNumberCardsChosenException
    Exception thrown when the number of cards chosen is different from the number of player
    InvalidPlayerIndexException
    Exception thrown when is tried to use a non valid player index
    InvalidPositionException
    Exception thrown when a Position has invalid values
    InvalidPutWorkerException
    Exception thrown when user try to put workers in occupied cells
    InvalidStateException
    Exception thrown when user try to make an action in a non valid state for that action
    MaxPlayersException
    Exception thrown when maximum number of player is reached is tried to add an other player
    MissingWorkerException
    Exception thrown when a player has less of two worker (it should not happens)
    NameAlreadyTakenException
    Exception thrown when a user try to use a nickname already taken
    NotAdjacentBuildingException
    Exception thrown when player try to build in a position not adjacent
    NotAdjacentMovementException
    Exception thrown when a player try to move on a position not adjacent
    NotEnoughGodsForPlayerException
    Exception thrown when gods chosen by godLike are not enough cause players are more
    NotPresentWorkerException
    Exception thrown when there is not a worker in the position selected
    NotPutTwoWorkerInSamePositionException
    Exception thrown when a player try to put a worker on the position of his other worker
    NotSelectedGodException
    Exception thrown when is tried to use a god not present in the gods chosen by godLike
    SameMovementException
    Exception thrown when someone call Cell::incrementLevel() on a occupied cell
    WrongAssociationViewPlayerException
    Exception thrown when a remote view does not corresponds to the related client
    WrongGodNameException
    Exception thrown when does not exist a god with the name supposed
